    "This results in an average area under the receicer operator characteristics curve (AUROC) of 0.9837 and an average area under the precision-recall curve (AUPRC) of 0.7707.",
    "For our final model, we replicate this procedure, by setting up a 5-fold CV on the entire dataset to find the best performing hyperparameters.",
    "We then train our RF on the entire dataset and use this model to identify bots and spam accounts in our dataset.",
    "As we are only interested in removing the most prevalent spam, we opt for a conservative removal strategy to not falsely remove too many real and non-spam users.",
    "Hence, we only remove users with a predicted bot probability >50% and more than 10 tweets since account creation as well as users with a predicted bot probability >30% and more than 10,000 tweets."
